{"tid":1510352,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"不如成立[監遊行會]","createTime":"2019-08-27T06:59:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T07:14:49.000Z","uid":280192,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fd442f759b5dde9d9f2dbaafe2c97771e5d60df9","tid":1510352,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:59:32.000Z","msg":"成立[監遊行會]模式：<br />\n1. 簡單來講，同監警會一9樣，安排30個&ldquo;各界代表&rdquo;，包括何韻詩、黃耀明、被打盲眼巴絲，國泰被炒員工等，自己友查自己友<br />\n2. 政府、警察對遊行人士有任何投訴，請先向監遊行會提交申請，我地會秉公辦理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成立[監遊會]好處：<br />\n<br />\n1. 以後政府有咩不滿，都有行之有效的投訴機制。林鄭個7樣再出來譴責暴徒衝擊，我地可以大大聲叫：向監遊會投訴啦！<br />\n<br />\n2. 警察再跳過我們的投訴程序，亂打亂捕，咪怪示威者還擊。要投訴示威者的話，請交出當時被冒犯的警察個人資料，謝謝。<br />\n<br />\n3.班藍絲廢老話對不合作運動有咩不滿，妨礙搵食等等，一9樣，你可以向監遊會投訴架。<br />\n<br />\n4. 搞得順利的話，推而廣之，遲d搞埋下議院。<br />\n<br />\n總括來講，比對家感受下咩叫制度暴力。"},{"pid":"17c17c53ff341bf4e0b8efb3fb4f37e77774c3f4","tid":1510352,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=c8027714\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=a10222b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi4GitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=5602cf7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/st